{"tid":544022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法律界選委批DQ周庭不合法不合憲","createTime":"2018-01-29T06:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T08:45:29.000Z","uid":20816,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d82798d69d841117a9adf1f9e6730610c8c29fd","tid":544022,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/520610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F520610&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ce23aa9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F520610&h=5885e8a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/520610</a><br />\n<br />\n法律界選委發表聯署聲明，批評選舉主任取消周庭參選資格的決定不合理、不合法亦不合憲。<br />\n<br />\n聯署的三十名法律界選委包括大律師公會主席戴啟思，以及前主席陳景生、梁家傑，對於選舉主任的決定表示遺憾，認為《基本法》及《人權法》保障香港永久居民有選舉權及被選權，但選舉主任基於政治聯繫剝奪周庭的被選權，是不合理、不合法亦不合憲，而且沒有給予周庭解釋的機會，有違自然公義的原則。"},{"pid":"c9938daa6ad2ef5fdf8084ba898f2640fd13e68e","tid":544022,"uid":17641,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"明黑鳩你，咁點？咁本事咪學朱元璋咁驅逐胡虜恢復中華囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ae81879e750425cd9b8cd27c62a1724bc61958","tid":544022,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"DQ梁天琦同陳浩天時你唔撚出聲?"},{"pid":"9f560e62d292a0abcd5cb55b26f8095db98e61d7","tid":544022,"uid":94591,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a6ae81879e750425cd9b8cd27c62a1724bc61958","tid":544022,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"DQ梁天琦同陳浩天時你唔撚出聲?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"起碼今次講番人話先<br />\n<br />\n定係你想睇到法律界赤化埋唔出聲???"},{"pid":"dd751cf703cde3b87ae1e16d5ca9d32ccf88ce10","tid":544022,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01